summary: "Hawk Tuah" is an internet meme that started with a 2024 YouTube video. Haliey Welch, a young woman from Nashville, used the phrase during a street interview. It's an onomatopoeia for spitting during oral sex. The video went viral, making Haliey famous online. She gained a following, started a business, and even threw a pitch at a New York Mets game. The meme turned into a big opportunity for her.
title: Hawk Tuah
